      The Radiant Complexion Index (RCI) is derived from a selection of beauty products featured in our catalog that rarely undergo price adjustments. Given their infrequent price changes, these items are believed to reflect expectations regarding future beauty trends more accurately than products with more frequent price revisions. A potential reason for stable prices could be the expenses associated with updating prices for these items. For further details on this concept, see our blog post: 'Timeless Beauty: Why Some Cosmetic Prices Stay Consistent.'
